{"tid":1655113,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【罷食行動升級】有建制選舉海報一律不光顧！！","createTime":"2019-10-15T02:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:37:57.000Z","uid":278414,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0067932f9e73564cc209192b1341a73ef69f1f62","tid":1655113,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請轉傳廣傳</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷食罷買係長期抗爭重要戰線之一。<br />\n區選將近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位手足<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>齊心協力</strong></span>，<br />\n自發由今天14/10/2019開始一個行動，<br />\n凡是商戶門口<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有民建聯、工聯會或是建制派選舉海報一律不光顧</span></span>！<br />\n送紅藍底店鋪一程同時，送埋建制派一程。<br />\n<br />\n明白堅持罷買罷食，講就易做就難。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>但每人出一分力，將可改變這個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n（p牌推唔到，麻煩幫推，謝謝🙏）<br />\n<br />\n【另加黃藍店鋪分佈資料<a href=\"https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restart-hk.com%2FShopList.html&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9JwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=73d18022\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html</a>】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfeZLzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfeZLzX.jpg&h=8da79687&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b9823c8c82c5edbd83ef47f44d2fb2f805a3eb6","tid":1655113,"uid":1562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:10:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06e00f2da65a47cf384bcec744a5bf1570adf479","tid":1655113,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9acd44efc8f774a5888933b05938